tafsir[85]{c,v,t}:
  40,1,"Haa, Miim: yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yewtanooma ka simoore Al Baqarah."
  40,2,"Jippinde Quraana ummaade e Alla Teddu…óo O hay gooto foolataa Mbo ganndu…óo maslahaaji jiyaa…ďe Makko e dow Nelaa…óo Makko."
  40,3,"Haforoowo junubaaji …óin, Ja…ďanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Sa…ótu…óo leptugol salii…óo tuubannde Mo, Jom neema yaaju…óo. Rewetee…óo e goonga alaa, si wanaa Kanko tun, ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden, √Ďalnde Darngal. O yo…ďa …ďe, ko …ďe hanndi kon."
  40,4,"Alaa ko wennjata e Aayeeje Allah …ďanngin…óe tawhiidi e goonga Nulaa…ďe …ďen, si wanaa yeddu…ďe Allah …ďen, sabu jii…ďagol haqille ma…ď…ďe. Wata a sunor hoditoraa, ko …ďe woni dillirde jawle e neemaaji. Ko …ďe nennitiranaa, ko hebilangol …ďe fewjana …ďe."
  40,5,"Ado …ďee …óoo, hari yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen fenniino Nulaa…ďe mun, feddeeji …óin …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe kadi fenni Aadi, e Samuuda, e yim…ďe Luutu …ďen, e wonndii…ďe Madyana …ďen e Fir'awna'en fow. Mofte kala e …ďen …óon, himmiri nanngugol Nulaa…óo mun on, fii warugol mo. ∆Āe wennjiri meere ma…ď…ďe, fii bonnitirgol nde goonga kan. Kono Mi nanngi …ďe. Tesko no nanngal Am wa…ótinirnoo e ma…ď…ďe. ∆äum ko lepte sa…ótu…óe wonunoo."
  40,6,"Ko wano Allah √Īaawiri non fii halkugol …óen mofte fennunoo…ďe Nulaa…ďe mun, Konngol Joomi maa ngol, an Nulaa…óo, jojjiri e yeddu…ďe …ďen: wonnde pellet, ko …ďe yim…ďe Yiite."
  40,7,"Malaa'ikaa…ďe ronndii…ďe Arsi Joomi maa kin, an Nulaa…óo, e …ďeya won…ďe sera makki, hi…ďe la…ď…ďina Joomi ma…ď…ďe, e kon ko hanndaa e Makko, …ďe gom…óina Mo, …ďe …óa…ď…ďira Mo, haforangol gom…óim…ďe Allah …ďen, …ďe wi'a: Joomi amen, ganndal Maa ngal e yurmeende Maa nden, yaajanii kala huunde. Yawtan tuubu…ďe …ďen, junuubi ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďen jokku…ďe diina Maa kan, da…óndaa …ďe kadi, Yiite ngen."
  40,8,"Mala'ika'en wi'a kadi: Joomi amen, naadu gom…óim…ďe …ďen ka Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, …óin …ói fodu…óaa …ďe, wa…ótidaa…ďe e kala mo∆ī∆īinno…óo golle, immorde e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, e genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, e …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, ko An woni Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, √Ďee√Īu…óo e e…ď…ďoore e toppitannde Mun."
  40,9,"Da…óndaa …ďe golle ma…ď…ďe bon…óe …óen, hara A nanngitiraali …ďe …óen. Kala non da…óndu…óaa …óum √Ďalnde Darngal, haray A yuminii mo. Ko …óum woni malal mawnungal ngal sugu mun alaa."
  40,10,"Yeddu…ďe e Nulaa…óo Makko on, noddoyte √Ďalnde Darngal, tuma …ďe naadaa ka Yiite, …ďe tikkana ko'e ma…ď…ďe, haa …ďe fe√Ī√Īina …óum, wonnde: ko tikkere Allah nden, …ďuri mawnude e dii ko tikkan…óon ko'e mon kon, tuma noddeteno…óon aduna, e fii gom…óingol Allah, yeddon Mo, kafidon Mo e rewetee…ói goo."
  40,11,"Yeddu…ď …ďen qirritoo junuubi ma…ď…ďe …óin, ka qirritagol tuuba nafataa, …ďe wi'a: joomi amen, A warii men laawi …ói…ói, tawde men woodanooko, tagu…óaa Men, refti waru…óaa men …ďaawo …óum. Wuurnitu…óaa men kadi laawi …ói…ói, ka tawnoo men woodanooka, e ka wuurnitu…óaa men …óon ummital. Haray men qirrike junuubi …ói men faggitii …óin. Taw si laawol no woodi, ka men yaltira e ngee Yiite, men yiltitoo aduna, fii mo∆ī∆īingol golle amen, ja…ďanaa men …óe?"
  40,12,"∆äen lepte …óe leptira…óon, ko sabu tawde si Allah tun noddanooma, hara O sirkanaaka, on yeddayno …óum, wa…óanon Mo kafidii…ói; si tawii non O kafidaama, gom…óinon. Awa √Īaawoore nden, ko Kanko tun heeranii, On Toowu…óo e Jaati Mun e Kattal Mun, Mawnu…óo e hoore kala huunde."
  40,13,"Ko Allah tun woni holliroowo on maandeeji Makko …óin, ka tatteeri(jookli) e ka wonkiiji, ko …ďannginana on, Kattal e Gootaagu Makko. O jippinirana on to…ďo ka kammu, fii ko arsikire…óon, immorde e pu…ói e remuruuji ewk. Alaa non waajitoroowo maandeeji Allah …óin, si wanaa tuuboowo la…ď…ďina, ruttoo e Makko on."
  40,14,"Onon …ďee gom…óim…ďe, rewiree Allah, la…ď…ďinirangol Mo dewal e toraare, hara on kafidaali Mo e go…ó…óum, hay si tawii …óum welataa heefer…ďe …ďen."
  40,15,"Ko Kanko hanndi heertinaneede toraare e …óoftaare, tawde ko O Jom darjaaji toowu…ói …ďanngi e kala tagu Makko ngun, Jey…óo Arsi maw…óo on. Himo jippinira wahayu on, e mo o muuyani e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, no pittaali ma…ď…ďe wuurira, …ďe wuurniira …óum wo…ó…ďe goo, e fii yo jertinir yim…ďe …ďen, √Ďalnde Darngal, nde aram…ďe e sakkitii…ďe hawroyta."
  40,16,"√Ďalnde …ďe fee√Īoyta nden, hara hi…ďe moo…ďondiri e nokku gooto. Huunde suu…óotaako Allah, e fii ma…ď…ďe, wanaa kam…ďe, wanaa golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, wanaa kadi njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin."
  40,17,"Hannde, wonkii kala yo…ďete ko feggitii e golle: woni mo∆ī∆īere maa bone. Too√Īe woo alaa hannde, tawde ko Allah √Īaawata, pellet, Allah ko yaawu…óo hasboore jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, tawde Himo hu…ďindii fii ma…ď…ďe."
  40,18,"Jertinir…ďe an Nulaa…óo, √Ďalaande Darngal nden, …ďadiinde, hewtunde. Tawde ko …ďadii fow, ko ko hewti. Nde √Īalnde, hakkee ko …ďer…óe …óen ngo∆īata, …óe ∆īawtiray ka konondol, hara …ďe waawataa haalude, si wanaa mo Allah duŇčanii e ma…ď…ďe. Too√Īirnoo…ďe sirku e geddi …ďen non, …ďe he…ďoytaa gi…óo maa musi…ó…óo, wanaa kadi tefoowo ja…ďantee…óo, si …ďe aru he…ďude on."
  40,19,"Allah no anndi ko gite …óen janforta e ndaar…óe, e ko …ďer…óe …óen suu…óata. Huunde e mun wirnaaki Mo."
  40,20,"Allah ko nun…óal √Īaawirta, O too√Īirtah go…ó…óo …óuytangol mo mo∆ī∆īi maa …ďeydangol mo bon…ói. ∆äin …ói sirkoo…ďe …ďen rewata ko wanaa Allah, hay huunde …ói √Īaawataa, tawde …ói jeyaa huunde. Pellet, ko Allah woni Nanoowo haala jeyaa…ďe Mun, Yi'oowo annuyeeji e kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe. O yo…ďitoya …ďe …óum."
  40,21,"Hara …ďee sirkoo…ďe yiilaaki ka leydi, …ďe taskoo no mofte fennunoo…ďe ado ma…ď…ďe …ďen wa'unoo? Ko battane bon…óe wonunoo. Hara le …ďeen no …ďurnoo …ďe tii…óude …ďe doole e batteeji accaa…ói ka leydi, wano kubeeje …óe …ďee ronki battinorde. Kono Allah halkitirno …ďe junuubi ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďe he…ďaano da…óndoowo …ďe e lepte Allah …óen."
  40,22,"Ko wa…ói kon …ďe leptaa, ko tawde Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addanayno …ďe hujjaaji …ďanngu…ói, immorde ka Allah, …ďe yedda Allah, …ďe fenna Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen. E ko …ďe doolnunoo kon fow, Allah naangiri …ďe lepte, O halki fii ma…ď…ďe, tawde pellet, ko O Doolnu…óo, Sa…ótu…óo leptugol yeddu…óo Mo, fenni Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  40,23,"Gom…óii Men nulirii Muusaa, Aayeeje Amen banngu…óe …óen, e hujja …ďanngu…óo."
  40,24,"Men nuli mo haa e Fir'awna, e jaagoraa…óo makko on Haamaana, e Qaaruuna. Kono …ďe wi'i: Muusaa, ko mbileejo, …óuu…óu…óo fenaande, e wi'ugol ko o Nulaa…óo."
  40,25,"Nde Muusaa addannoo…ďe hujjaaji …ďanngin…óo goonga makko kan, Fir'awna wi'i:waree …ďi…ó…ďe gom…óimdim…ďe …ďen e makko, heddon rew…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, hoynugol …ďe. Kono ko heefer…ďe …ďen fewjirta …óuytugol limoore gom…óim…ďe …ďen wonaali, si wanaa mulata yaha, hara batte alanaa …óum."
  40,26,"Fir'awana wi'i: Accee mi wara Muusaa, fii yaggingol mo, e no o noddira Joomi makko, fii ha…óugol lam …óum. Min mi haajaaka e …óum. Mi hulu wata o waylu diina mon kan, maa o fe√Ī√Īina bonnere ka leydi, woni warugol e bonnital."
  40,27,"Nde Fir'awna gaynunoo kammbude, Annabai Muusaa maakani mo: Mi moolorii da…óndiragol Jey…óo lam On, jeyi on, e bone mawnintinanii…óo goonga e gom…óinal, mo gom…óinaa √Ďalnde Darngal, e hasboore e lepte ko woni ton."
  40,28,"Gorko goo, gom…óin…óo Allah, jeyaa…óo e yim…ďe fir'awna …ďen, suu…óunoo…óo yim…ďe mun, gom…óinal makko ngal, salii…óo fellitgol ma…ď…ďe warugol Muusa ngol, o wi'i: E on waray gorko mo bonnaa, si wanaa fii o wi'i: Ko Allah woni Joomi am? Hara le o addanii on hujjaaji e …ďannganduyeeji, sembinay…ói goonga makko kan, wiide ko O nulaa…óo Joomi makko? Si tawii ko o fenu…óo, haray lorra fenaande makko nden, ko e makko yantata; si tawii non ko goongu…óo, haray yoga e ko o kammbirani on kon e lepte aduna …óen, he…ďay on. Pellet, Allah fewanataa e goonga, on taw…óo no yawti keeri Allah …óin, fefindii fenaande, baki e Makko, Kanko e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  40,29,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, laamu no woodani on hanndi, hi…óon fooli e leydi Misra ndin. Kono ko hommbo da…óndata en, e lepte Allah …óen, si …óe arii e men, tuma waru…óen Muusaa? Fir'awna wi'i: Ko feere am nde mi √Īaawi nden, jokketee. Mi yi'ii feere warugol Muusaa, fii ha…óugol bone e bonnere. Mi tinndintaa on, si wanaa sawaaba."
  40,30,"Gom…óin…óo on laa…ďani reedu, o wi'itani yim…ďe makko …ďen: min on mi…óo hulani on - si tawii on arii Muusaa e hoore too√Īe e jaggitere - lepte, sugu lepte yim…ďe feddeeji …ďen, ha…ďunoo…ďe Nulaa…ďe mun adinoo…ďe, Allah halki …ďe."
  40,31,"Wano mbowka yeddaynoo…ďe fenna Nulaa…ďe …ďen, sugu yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e arunoo…ďe …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe …ďen. Allah halkirno …ďe, yeddugol ma…ď…ďe fenna Nulaa…ďe …ďen. Allah non faandanaaki jeyaa…ďe …ďen, too√Īe. Ko junuubi ma…ď…ďe, O leptirta …ďe, njo…ďdi hawrondindi e golle ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  40,32,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, min mi…óo hulani on, √Ďalnde Darngal: nden √Ďalaande, nde yim…ďe …ďen noddindiroyta, sabu …ďadandiral maa jaahu, sikkugol …ďe …óum nafay nden √Ďalnde hul…ďiniinde."
  40,33,"√Ďalnde huccitiroyton, dugugol, sabu kulol Yiite ngen, hara da…óndoowo on e lepte Allah …óen, alanaa on nden √Ďalnde. Kala mo Allah hoyfii fii mun, O …óawi mo gom…óingol, haray fewoowo mo alaa. Tawde ko Allah tun fewnata."
  40,34,"Gom…óii Yuusufu ardaniino on ko adii, e hujjaaji …ďanngin…ói wootin…óingol Allah, kono on seeraano e sikkitagol fenna, kon ko o addani on. Haa nde o faatinoo, …ďeydu…óon sikkitagol, wi'u…óon. Allah nultataa Nulaa…óo goo, …ďaawo makko. Ko wano majjir…óon nii e goonga kan, Allah majjinirta kala yawtoowo keeri Allah …óin, sikkitii…óo e gootaaku Makko."
  40,35,"∆Āen wenjiroo…ďe Aayeeje Allah …óen, fii bonnitirgol …óe ko aldaa e hujja ar…óo …ďe, kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen mawnii tikkere mun ka Allah, e ka gom…óim…ďe Mo gom…óini Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Ko wano Allah notiri non e …ďer…óe …ďee wenjoo…ďe …óoo …ďen, O notirta e …ďernde kala mawnintinanii…óo goonga, dundarankeejo feewnetaake e peewal maa e jam."
  40,36,"Fir'awna wi'ani jaagoraa…óo makko on Haaamaana: Ko an yo Haamaana, mahanam soorooru toowundu, no gasa ka mi yottoo …óate …óen."
  40,37,"Fii no mi yottora e laawi ∆īawru…ói …óin ka kammuuli, mi ∆īeewa Rewetee…óo Muusaa, On mo o aa∆īii wiide On ko Rewetee…óo e goonga, sabu mi…óo sikki ko o fenoowo. Ko wano non Fir'awna cu…óiranaa, kuu…óe makko bon…óe …óen, no de …óa…ď…ďiraynoo Haamaana, wa…óugol …óum; o sakkaa e laawol goonga ngol, o heddii e laawol majjere ngol. Feere Fir'awna nden non - e fii fe√Ī√Īingol meere makko nden, bonnita goonga Muusaa kan - wonaali, si wanaa e hayrere, tawde ko nimse e sooyugol ko sakkitori, e makiseede poomaa."
  40,38,"Gorko gom…óin…óo, jeyaa…óo e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen, woni e laa…ďangol reedu, o wi'i: Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, jokkee lam, mi tinndina on, laawol sawaaba e peewal ngol."
  40,39,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, anndee …óam nguurndam aduna, ko dakamme da∆īondiray…óo, wata …óum hodu on. Anndon ko laakara on, e neemaaji makko duumotoo…ói …óin, woni galle √Īii…ďal …óen. Golliranee …óen …óon, …óoftagol Allah, rentoo e soklirgol nguurndam mon aduna, yejjiton gollangol laakara."
  40,40,"Mo gollii ko boni, o yo…ďitetaake, si wanaa yeru …óum, o …ďeydantaake lepte e mun; kala kadi gollu…óo ko mo∆ī∆īi, hara ko fii Allah, woni gorko maa debbo, hara ko gom…óin…óo Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ďen …óon e sifaaji ma…ď…ďe yettinii…ói …óin, …ďe naatoyay Aljanaa, √Ďalnde Darngal, …ďe arsikoyee ton: kon ko Allah fodunoo…ďe e dim…óe, e neemaaji duumii…ói, …ói ta∆īondirtaa, ko aldaa e limoore."
  40,41,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, ko wa…ói si mi…óo nodda on e da…óirgol hayrude aduna e laakara, gom…óinde Allah, golla ko mo∆ī∆īi, onon, hi…óon noddira lam naatugol Yiite, …óa…ď…ďirgol lam, yeddugol Allah?"
  40,42,"Hi…óon noddira lam e meere mon nden, jortagol no mi yeddira Allah, mi kafida Mo e go…ó…óum goo, ko mi alanaa …óum ganndal, hara non, min mi…óo noddude on e gom…óingol Allah, Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, Surroowo bakkaatu, Mawnu…óo haforangol jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  40,43,"Tigi on, ko noddoton lam e mun kon, gom…óingol …óoftoo, noddaandu goonga woo alanaa …óum aduna, wanaa laakara, gooto kadi noototaakau ndun noddaandu. E wonnde pellet, ruttorde men nden, en fow, ko ka Allah tun, e wonnde fantim…ďe geddi …ďen, ko …ďen woni yim…ďe Yiite …ďen, duumotoo…ďe ton, √Ďalnde Darngal."
  40,44,"∆Āe salii laa…ďal makko reedu ngal, o wi'ani …ďe: aray nde anndoton, fii ko mi laa…ďani on reedu kon, nimson salaare mon nden; min non, mi fawii fiyaaku am on fow, e Allah Gooto On. Pellet, huunde suu…óaaki Allah, e golle jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  40,45,"Allah da…óndi mo, boneeji …ói …ďe fewjunannoo mo …óin, fii warugol mo, O huu…ďitiri yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen, lepte yoolagol. Allah yooli mo kanko Fir'awna, e konu ma…ď…ďe ngun fow."
  40,46,"Caggal …ďe maayii, …ďe wee…ďitoyte e Yiite ngen, ka genaale ma…ď…ďe, bimmbi e kiikii…óe. √Ďalnde Darngal darotoo (wi'oyte): Naadee jokkunoo…ďe Fir'awna …ďen, ka …ďuri sa…ótude e lepte. Sabu ko …ďe yeddiraynoo kon, …ďe fenna …ďe falatoo e laawol Allah ngol."
  40,47,"Janto an Nulaa…óo, tuma jokkunoo…ďe …ďen yeddondiroyta e jokkanoo…ďe …ďen, ka nder Yiite, …ďe wi'ana …ďen jokkonoo…ďe towninitinoo…ďe: Menen, ko onon men jokkunoo aduna, e majjere, taw si on duncanay men ge…ďal e lepte Allah …óen, ronnditano…óon men …óe?"
  40,48,"Townitinii…ďe jokkanoo…ďe …ďen kadi wi'a: En fow mee…óen, jokkunoo…ďe e jokkanoo…ďe fow, hino e Yiite ngen, gooto ronnditantaako go…ó…óo goo, ge…ďal e lepte laakara …óen. Tawde pellet, Alah √Īaawii hakkunde jeyaa…ďe …ďen. O yo…ďiti kala e ko hanndi e mun kon."
  40,49,"Wonaa…ďe lepteede …ďen ka Yiite fow wi'ana Malaa'ika'en, ayninaa…ďe Yiite ngen, tuma …ďe ta∆īii yaltugol e magge, ruttoo aduna, fii tuubugol: Toranee men Joomi mon, O hoynana men √Īalaande wootere, e …óee lepte duumii…óe."
  40,50,"Ayninaa…ďe Jahannama …ďen jaaboo heefer…ďe …ďen: Nulaa…ďe mon …ďen ardanaano on e hujjaaji …ďanngu…ói? Heefer…ďe …ďen wi'a: oo'owoye ! ∆Āe arduno e mun few ! Malaa'ika'en jaabitoo: awa toree, onon tigiri. Menen men tefantaa keefeero. Kono toraare heefer…ďe …ďen wonaali, si wanaa e meere. Tawde …ďe ja…ďirantaake, sabu keeferaaku ma…ď…ďe ngun."
  40,51,"Pellet, Men wallay Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen, e gom…óim…ďe Allah e Nulaa…ďe Mun …ďen, aduna …óoo, …ďanngingol hujjaajii ma…ď…ďe …óin, foolna …ďe e ay…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen. Men walliroya …ďe kadi √Ďalnde Darngal, naadugol …ďe Aljanna, leptira yeddondiraynoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe aduna …ďen, naatugol Yiite, …ďaawo nde Annabaa…ďe e Malaa'ikaa…ďe e gom…óim…ďe …ďen fow seeditaade, wonnde Nule …óen yottino e mofte …óen."
  40,52,"√Ďalnde nde too√Īunoo…ďe geddi e keeferaaku …ďen nafiroytaa hoore-ma…ď…ďe, ngatinagol, hara kuddi Allah no woodani …ďe nden √Īalnde, e galle bon…óe ka laakara, ka …ďe hawroyta e lepte muusu…óe."
  40,53,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa ganndal, ngal o fewnirta …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen, e goonga, Men wa…ói Tawreetaare nden, Deftere roneteende, hakkunde …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen."
  40,54,"Ko nde fewnaynde e goonga, e waaju wonannde joomiraa…ďe haqqille hisu…óe …ďen."
  40,55,"An Nulaa…óo, mu√Ī√Īo e ko yim…ďe maa fennata maa, …ďe lorre, sabu pellet, ko Allah fodu maa e ballal e semmbineede kon, ko goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un. Insinoraa fii haforaneede junuubi maa …óin, subbunhinoraa yettugol Joomi maa, gila irfaj, haa mir."
  40,56,"Pellet,wennjiroo…ďe e Aayeeje Allah …óen,fii bonnitirgol …óe ko aldaa e hujja wanaa daliil,ko fii tun faale townitagol mawnintinanoo goonga kan, kono …ďe hewtataa e ko …ďe faalaa kon.An Nulaa…óo,moolor Allah,tawde pellet,ko Kanko woni Nanoowo haalaaji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen,Yi'oowo kuu…óema…ď…ďe.Huunde e …óin suu…óaaki Mo,O yo…ďitoyay …ďe …óum."
  40,57,"Pellet, ko tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, sabu cemmbe e ya√Īji majji, …ďuri mawnude e dii tagugol yim…ďe …ďen. Tagir…óo …ói mawneendi majji On, ko hattan…óo wuurnitugol maay…ďe, fii √Īaawugol …ďe yo…ďita …ďe. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe anndaa, sakko …ďe waajitora …óum, …ďe wa…óa …óum dalil, e fii ummital."
  40,58,"Bun…óo fotataa e yi'oowo, wanaa gom…óim…ďe Allah …ďen, goongini Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen, …ďe mo∆ī∆īini golle, woni ko fotata e bonnir…óo golle mun, finnde bonnde e geddi. Kono on waajitortaa, si wanaa see…óa. Tawde si …óon waajitoraynoo ko yoni, on anndayno ko senndi …ďen …ói…óo, fii no yaccoron wa'ude wa gom…óim…ďe golli mo∆ī∆īu…ói yamiraa…ói …óin, no jortoron weleyee Allah."
  40,59,"Pellet, Darngal, ngal Allah wuurnitata maay…ďe …ďen e mun, fii √Īaawugol …ďe yo…ďa, ko ko arata, feere mun alaa, sikka alaa e …óum. Kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe gom…óinaa …óum. Ko …óum ha…ói …ďe hebilanagol nden √Īalnde"
  40,60,"Joomi mon, onon yim…ďe …ďen, daali: heertinanee Lam, Min tun, dewal e toraare, Mi jaabinana on toraare mon, Mi yawtana on, Mi yurmina on. Mawnintinantoo…ďe …óum …ďen, ko pellet, √Ďalnde Darngal, …ďe naatoyay Jahannama, ko …ďe hoy…ďe jaasinaa."
  40,61,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo on jemma on, ni…ď…ďitir…óo, fii ka dee∆īon fowto…óon e mun, O wa…óirani on nyalorma on, ndaygin…óo, fii ka gollon e mun. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ďural mawngal e yim…ďe …ďen, tawde O timminirii neemaaji Makko …óin e ma…ď…ďe, no fee√Īiri e no wirnori. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe yettataa Allah, e naamaaji Makko …óin, dow ma…ď…ďe."
  40,62,"Ko On moo…óon Allah, wa…óan…óo on …óin neemaaji, woni Tagu…óo kala huunde. Wanaa go…ó…óo goo. Rewtee…óo e goonga alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko honno ferlisora…óon gaay e rewugol Mo, jokka rewugol ko nafataa lorrataa?"
  40,63,"Ko wano …ďee …óoo ferlisoraa non e gom…óingol Allah rewa Mo Kanko tun, …ďeya yeddaynoo…ďe Aayeeje Allah tindinay…ói fii tawhiidi on, ferlisortenoo e kala jamaanu, …ďe feewataano e goonga, …ďe hawrataano e sawaaba."
  40,64,"Ko Allah woni wa…óan…óo on, onon yim…ďe …ďen, ndii leydi, dunngal √Īii…ďirgal mon, O wa…ói kammu ngun, √Īe√Īaangu dow mon, hara yanataa e mon, O mbaadini on ka renngaaji yumma mon'en - O mo∆ī∆īini mbaadiiji mon, - O arsiki on laa…ďu…ói dagii…ói. Ko On moo…óon, neeminir…óo on …óum, woni Allah Joomi mon. Senaare heewii e Jey…óo tageefo ngon fow. Rewetee…óo alanaa ngo, si wanaa Kanko senii…óo On."
  40,65,"Ko Kanko woni wuur…óo Mo maayataa On. rewetee…óo e goonga alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Noddiree Mo dewal e toraare; faando…óon Mo Kanko tun, hara on kafidaali Mo e taguuji Makko goo. Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo tageefo ngon."
  40,66,"Maaku an Nulaa…óo: min, Allah ha…óii lam rewugol, …óin …ói rewoton, hara wanaa Allah; sanamuuji …ói nafataa, …ói lorrataa. Mi ha…óa …óum, nde hujjaaji …óin arunoo e am, fii …ďanngingol meere rewugol …óin. Allah yamiri lam kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo Mo, Kanko tun, ka dewal. Tawde ko Kanko woni Jey…óo tageefo ngon fow. Jey…óo ngo alaa, si wanaa Kanko."
  40,67,"Ko Kanko tagiri ben mon Aadam, immorde e mbulmbulndi, refti O tagiri on …ďaawo …óum, e to…ď…ďere maniiyu, refti e he…ó…óere ∆īii∆īam, refti …ďaawo …óum, O yaltiniri on e deedi neeniraa…ďe mon …ďen, entoy tokosoy, fii no yottoron cukaaku ngun, mawnon haa wonton nayee…ďe, - kono hara wo…ó…ďe e mo'on, maayay ado …óum, - haa no yottoron dumunna happaa…óo ka Allah, mo …óuytotaako …ďeydotaako, belajo'o, ka nafitoron …óii hujjaaji fii anndugol kattal e gootaagu Allah ngun."
  40,68,"Ko Kanko Allah tun, woni wuurnoowo, e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anay mo tun: ""wonu"", o wona."
  40,69,"A tinaali, an Nulaa…óo, …ďen wennjondirtee…ďe e Aayeeje Allah …óen, fennoo…ďe …óe, e hoore ko …óe fee√Īi kon? a Ňčal…óay e ma…ď…ďe, e ko …ďe …óuurnotoo e goonga kon, hoore ko ka fee√Īi kon."
  40,70,"∆Āen fennu…ďe Alqur'aana, e ko Men immindini kon e Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen, immorde e goonga, aray ka …ďen fennoo…ďe annda, battane e bone mun."
  40,71,"∆Āe anndoyay battane fennugol ma…ď…ďe ngol, tuma nde kolmboyaa ka daa…óe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe jolkiree ka koy…óe, halfinaa…ďe lepte …óen daasa …ďe."
  40,72,"∆Āe ndaasee e ndiyam wul…óam haa fati, refti …ďe hu…ď…ďee Yiite ngen."
  40,73,"Refti …ďe feliree wi'aneede: ko honto woni rewetee…ói mon, …ói aa∆īino…óon wonnde on sirkiranii…ói dewal?"
  40,74,"Ko honto …óin sanamuuji, …ói rewayno…óon, hara wanaa Allah, …ói nafataa …ói lorrataa? Heefer…ďe …ďen jaaboo: ∆äi majjitorike men. Wurin, men wonaano aduna, e rewugol ko hanndunoo e reweede. Ko wano …ďee …óoo majjiri non, Allah majjinirta yeddu…ďe goonga …ďen, e kala nokku e jamaanu."
  40,75,"∆Āe wi'anee : ko fawi on …óee lepte, ko sabu ko weltorayno…óon kon, sirku on, e ko wewlayno…óon kon fantinon."
  40,76,"Natiree dame Jahannama …óen, luttugol ton poomaa. Nge bonii jaa∆īorde townitanii…ďe goonga …ďen."
  40,77,"Mu√Ī√Īo, an Nulaa…óo, e ko yim…ďe maa lorrete …ďe fenne kon. Pellet, ko Allah fodu maa wallude kon, ko goonga, mo sikke alaa e mu'un. Ko si Men holle yoga e ko Men kammbirani …ďe kon e lepte, e nguurndam maa, wano fe∆ī∆īirnoo ka hare Badri, maa hara Men ∆īettite ado mun, fow e mun, ko ka Amen tun, woni ruttorde ma…ď…ďe, √Ďalnde Darngal, Men yo…ďa …ďe golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, Men naatna…ďe ka Yiite, …ďe lutta ton poomaa."
  40,78,"Gom…óii Men imminii Nulaa…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe, haa e yim…ďe mun, ado maa, an Nulaa…óo. ∆Āen fenni …ďe, …ďe lorri …ďe. Kono …ďe mu√Ī√Īii e …óin fow. Hino e …ďen Nulaa…ďe, …ďe Men fillani maa fii mun; hino e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Men fillanaaki ma fii mun. Haananaa Nulaa…óo woo, nde o addanta yim…ďe makko …ďen Aaya, immorde e Joomi makko, si wanaa hara ko e duŇčayee Makko. Ko heefer…ďe …ďen lamndotoo mofte ma…ď…ďe …óen addugol Aaya, ko too√Īe. Si yamiroore Allah fii √Īaawugol sennda hakkunde Nulaa…ďe …ďen e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen arii, ko nun…óal √Īaawirtee. Heefer…ďe …ďen halkee, Nulaa…ďe …ďen da…óndee; nden √Īalnde, yim…ďe meere …ďen sooyira yollugol ko'e ma…ď…ďe e halkaare, sabu keeferaaku ma…ď…ďe ngun."
  40,79,"Ko Allah woni wa…óan…óo on geloo…ói …óin, e na'i …óin e dammi …óin, ko wa…ó…óoron yoga e majji, √Īaamon tebbeeli yoga majji."
  40,80,"Hino woodani on e …óii neemoraa…ói, nafooreeji …óuu…óu…ói, hey…óitay…ói jamaanu kala. Hi…óon he…ďira …ói, kala ko faalete…óon e haajuuji, wano setagol ka njorndi e ka maayo."
  40,81,"Allah no holla on maandeeji tindinay…ói e kattal e gootaagu Makko ngun. E ko hon…óum e maandeeji Allah …óin, woni yeddoton, …ďaawo nde yanana…óon, wonnde ko …ói maandeeji Makko?"
  40,82,"E …ďee fennoo…ďe yiilaaki ka leydi, …ďe taskoo ko honno battane …óeya mofte fennunoo…ďe ado ma…ď…ďe wattinirnoo, …ďe waajitora …óum? Gom…óii …óen mofte no …ďurnoo …ďe jawle e cemmbe, …ďe …ďuri …ďe batteeji accaa…ói ka leydi. Kono kon ko …ďe faggotonoo e cemmbe, duncanaano …ďe go…ó…óum, nde lepte Allah …óen arunoo halkugol …ďe."
  40,83,"Nde Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addaanno…ďe hujjaaji …ďanngu…ói …óin, …ďe fenni …ói, …ďe welaa jogitagol ganndal ko woni ka ma…ď…ďe kon, lunndiingal ko Nulaa…ďe …ďen addani …ďe kon. Ontuma, …ďe huu…ďitiraa lepte …óe …ďe jalkitaynoo …óen, si Nulaa…ďe …ďen hul…ďiniriino …ďe …óe."
  40,84,"Nde …ďe yi*unoo lepte Amen …óen, …ďe ja…ďi ka ja…ďugol nafataa, …ďe wi'i: Men gom…óinii Allah tun, men yeddii …óin kafidaa…ói e sanamuuji …ói men rewaynoo, hara wanaa Kanko."
  40,85,"Kono gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe wonaAno ko nafata …ďe, fewndo …ďe haccinoo lepte Amen …óen no jippoo e ma…ď…ďe; …óum ko laawol yawtunoongol e jayaa…ďe Makko …ďen, wonnde gom…óinal nafataa …ďe, tuma …ďe yi'i lepte …óen. Yeddu…ďe …ďen sooyiniri ko'e-ma…ď…ďe …óon nden √Īalnde, nde …ďe halkiranoo sabu ko …ďe yeddiri kon Allah, …ďe salii tuubude ado …ďe yi'ude lepte …óen."
